ght=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-email.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-printer.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111231-north-korea-136478028.html#comments\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-comments.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.google.com/buzz/post?message=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A5%9D%E8%B4%BA%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E6%8B%85%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9D%E9%B2%9C%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%86%9B%E4%BA%8B%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E4%BA%BA&#038;url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111231-north-korea-136478028.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-googleBuzz.png\" /></a></li>\n<li>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://twitthis.com/twit?url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111231-north-korea-136478028.html&#038;title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A5%9D%E8%B4%BA%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E6%8B%85%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9D%E9%B2%9C%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%86%9B%E4%BA%8B%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E4%BA%BA\"></a></li>\n<li>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>朝鲜年轻的新领导人正得到来自邻国中国的支持。</p>\n<p>中国国家主席胡锦涛向金正恩发出贺电，祝贺金正恩担任朝鲜最高军事领导人。</p>\n<p>中国政府的网站公布了这封贺信，信中说，中朝两国有着深厚的传统友谊。信中还说，两国关系一定会进一步加深。</p>\n<p>平壤与北京的关系非常重要，因为朝鲜依赖中国的贸易和援助。</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h4>相关文章</h4>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/cantonese/news/NORTH_KOREA-136473263.html\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"90\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/images/90*90/AP_Korea_Kim_29dec11_230.jpg\" width=\"90\" /></a><br />\n<h3><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/cantonese/news/NORTH_KOREA-136473263.html\">北韓正式任命金正恩為最高統帥</a> <img align=\"top\" border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-media-audio.gif\" width=\"14\" /><img align=\"top\" border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-media-comment-gray.gif\" width=\"12\" /></h3>\n<p>北韓正式任命金正恩為武裝部隊最高統帥﹐確立了他在父親金正日去世後的權威。北韓國家通訊社朝中社星期六宣佈這個決定時說﹐金正恩是在北韓勞動黨中央委員會政治局的一次會議上得到這個頭銜的。</p>\n<div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-email.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-printer.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111231-north-korea-136478028.html#comments\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-comments.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.google.com/buzz/post?message=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A5%9D%E8%B4%BA%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E6%8B%85%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9D%E9%B2%9C%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%86%9B%E4%BA%8B%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E4%BA%BA&#038;url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111231-north-korea-136478028.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-googleBuzz.png\" /></a></li>\n<li>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://twitthis.com/twit?url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111231-north-korea-136478028.html&#038;title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A5%9D%E8%B4%BA%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E6%8B%85%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9D%E9%B2%9C%E6%9C%80